Hey everyone! I am beyond excited to share some news with you all. I have just created a brand new podcast t-shirt that's now available for purchase! 🎧👕🦋

This shirt means so much to me because it's not just a piece of clothing – it's a symbol of conquering fear. As someone who has struggled with anxiety and self-doubt, starting my own podcast was a huge leap out of my comfort zone. But it's also been one of the most rewarding experiences of my life.

I hope that by wearing this t-shirt, you'll be reminded that it's okay to be scared, but that you shouldn't let fear hold you back from chasing your dreams. This shirt is a way to show your support for the amazing community that we are building together.

If you're interested in checking out the shirt, head to the link in bio. And thank you so much for your support – it means the world to me! Let's all kiss fear goodbye and go after our dreams. ❤️ #kissfeargoodbye

Today marks 1 year, 1 month, and 2 days ( yes, I’m one of those that counts to the dot now 😝) of my sober journey. It’s a testament to the strength within, proving that we can give up anything when we commit to it. I share this not to influence anyone’s choices or lifestyles, but simply to celebrate the victories, both big and small, and to embrace the power we hold to create positive change in our lives.
